This paper discusses the use of web archives, which is a topic related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions text analysis, which falls under computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of classifiers to predict the semantic category of a collection is related to machine learning (cs.CY) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Overall, the paper covers a range of topics that could fit into multiple sub-categories, but the most relevant ones are likely cs.DL and cs.IR.
